u are the one. The only one. And you always will be.', 6569, 0), (33829, 'You loved him enough to let him leave… Now you need to love yourself enough to let him go.', 6569, 0), (33830, 'Some of the best things that have ever happened to us wouldn’t have happened to us, if it weren’t for some of the worst things that have ever happened to us.', 4616, 0), (33831, 'Grit is the persistence in following your own destiny', 6397, 0), (33832, 'Stop looking to others for inspiration. Stop looking at past accomplishments. Be your own inspiration today and for tomorrow.', 5284, 0), (33833, 'There’s no such thing as a good or bad person: there are just people who have each been or seem to have been good or bad to you, someone, or some people, thus far.', 4616, 0), (33834, 'When we share, we open doors to a new beginning.', 6397, 0), (33835, 'Some people will insult your intelligence by suddenly being nice or nicer to you once you make it … or they think you have.', 4616, 0), (33836, 'Jangan katakan ''aku mencintaimu''. Kita hanya dua makhluk kesepian yang dipertautkan oleh keadaan. Dan keadaan akan selalu berubah.', 8488, 0), (33837, 'We seldom learn much from someone with whom we agree.', 4616, 0), (33838, 'Embracing weakness echoes resilience.', 6397, 0), (33839, 'Most adults are knowledgeable to a child, but ignorant for their age.', 4616, 0), (33840, 'Forgiveness is brave, sets us free from darkness, and allows light to shine the sweet fragrance of life into our souls', 6397, 0), (33841, 'Most women would each be left with fewer dreams or without a dream, if the institution of marriage were to be abolished.', 4616, 0), (33842, 'Some writers write to forget. Some forget to write.', 4616, 0), (33843, 'Kau tak boleh mengukur kemampuan seseorang dari usianya.', 8488, 0), (33844, 'O'' melancholy,hectic chill for human soul,herewith dismal presence,any spirit does descent.', 8489, 0), (33845, 'Terlambat adalah dosa besar menurut ukuran Swedia. Apa pun alasannya.', 8488, 0), (3384